Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: Meeting the Monster
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cstzb8
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 25 Sep 2017
Ugandan Betty Bigombe made it her life mission to try and broker peace between the Ugandan government and the Lord's Resistance Army which was led by Joseph Kony. He was known around the world for abducting children to use as soldiers and sex slaves. Rene Denfeld is a Death Row investigator from Oregon in the United States, she has come face to face with some of the most violent criminals in the country but her biggest monster was the man she called her father. Image: Drawing of girl facing death Credit: sSplajn/GETTY IMAGES Show less